PIDSource and PIDOutput were <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deprecation#Software" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">deprecated</a> in 2020, and they’ll be removed in 2023. Just call the relevant getter directly and pass it into the PIDController, like so: 
import com.revrobotics.CANSparkMax;
import edu.wpi.first.math.PIDController;
import edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.TimedRobot;
import edu.wpi.&hellip;
